<item>
            <title>[LU-257] lustre.spec.in utilises undefined macro krequires</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-257</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lustre.spec.in references undefined `krequires&apos; macro for required kernel version. Patch included reverts this back to `kversion&apos; macro to allow for complete installs after successful builds.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
